{"tid":380781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 點樣擺脱無腦煩膠","createTime":"2017-08-30T11:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T11:46:24.000Z","uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cba94b83fc711f8704ed6b47f3d35a35c8b28424","tid":380781,"uid":137178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:34:24.000Z","msg":"我去迎新日<br />\n 入個hall聽佢介紹迎新之類<br />\n坐我旁邊有個肥仔潦我傾計 <br />\n我答左佢一句 點知係惡夢既開始<br />\n成程煩膠住我 我初頭以為佢係d鐘意傾計既人<br />\n就無點理 <br />\n慢慢聽得出佢係d憨鳩無腦既人<br />\n成程認屎認屁 以為自己聰明 搞笑<br />\n我開始唔理佢但無用  <br />\n轉地方又成程跟住我 <br />\n結果比佢煩足3個鐘<br />\n最後走個時先賣甩佢<br />\n<br />\n各位ching點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢好似當左我係朋友 係咁問我名 我無答佢 <br />\n我同佢讀同一科 我唔想成個學期比人破壞哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71c2e5dd87c6eb44f84adee1d0cb44832a81a8f","tid":380781,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}